        "action": "Extend the Gambling Act to cover Loot Boxes",
        "additional_details": "The well known game publisher, EA have referred to it as a \u2018surprise mechanic\u2019, which changes nothing about the system, and believes it is not unethical to continue using it. However, I and I\u2019m sure many people would people would agree it is very unethical and should be properly regulated.",
        "background": "I would like the government to extend the Gambling Act to cover \u2018loot box\u2019 systems from computer games so they are regulate in the same way as other forms of gambling. These systems can lead to gambling addiction and children spending too much money on these \u2018loot boxes\u2019 in games.",
